<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome - Sustainable Market</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #e6e9ef;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
            color: #444b40;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .welcome-card {
            background-color: #e6e9ef;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            box-shadow: 20px 20px 60px #b8bcc2, -20px -20px 60px #ffffff;
            padding: 5rem 2.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 950px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .text-contrast {
            color: #2c3e50 !important;
        }

        /* Logo Box with Image */
        .main-logo-box {
            width: 140px;
            height: 140px;
            margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
            background-color: #e6e9ef;
            border-radius: 40px;
            box-shadow: 10px 10px 20px #b8bcc2, -10px -10px 20px #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .main-logo-img {
            max-width: 100%;
            max-height: 100%;
            object-fit: contain;
            filter: drop-shadow(2px 2px 4px rgba(184, 188, 194, 0.6));
        }

        /* Action Cards (Consumer / Market) */
        .action-card {
            background-color: #e6e9ef;
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            height: 100%;
            text-decoration: none !important;
            display: block;
            box-shadow: 8px 8px 16px #b8bcc2, -8px -8px 16px #ffffff;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        .action-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 15px 15px 30px #b8bcc2, -15px -15px 30px #ffffff;
            border-color: rgba(55, 141, 252, 0.2);
        }

        .action-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            display: block;
        }

        /* Buttons */
        .btn-morph {
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 14px 50px;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-morph-primary {
            background-color: #378dfc;
            color: white !important;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 15px rgba(55, 141, 252, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-morph-primary:hover {
            background-color: #2e7ae0;
            box-shadow: 7px 7px 20px rgba(55, 141, 252, 0.5);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-morph-light {
            background-color: #e6e9ef;
            color: #7f8a99 !important;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 10px #b8bcc2, -5px -5px 10px #ffffff;
        }

        .btn-morph-light:hover {
            box-shadow: inset 3px 3px 6px #b8bcc2, inset -3px -3px 6px #ffffff;
        }

        .footer-info {
            margin-top: 5rem;
            opacity: 0.7;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container hero-section">
        <div class="welcome-card">
            
            <div class="main-logo-box">
                <img src="/img/leaf.png" alt="GreenMarkt Logo" class="main-logo-img">
            </div>

            <h1>
                <span class="text-success">Green<span class="text-body">Markt</span> </span>
            </h1>

            <p class="lead text-muted mb-5 px-md-5">
                Stop food waste and start saving. Access local discounted products and contribute to a greener planet today.
            </p>

            <div class="row g-4 mb-5 text-start">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <a href="/main" class="action-card">
                        <i class="bi bi-cart-check-fill action-icon text-primary"></i>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold text-contrast">I am a Consumer</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Discover discounted products near you, fill your cart, and prevent waste.</p>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <a href="/market/dashboard" class="action-card">
                        <i class="bi bi-shop action-icon text-success"></i>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold text-contrast">I am a Seller</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Manage your inventory, list products nearing expiration, and reach local buyers.</p>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4 border-top border-light d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row justify-content-center gap-3">
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-morph btn-morph-primary">Login</a>
                <a href="/register" class="btn btn-morph btn-morph-light">Join Us</a>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-info">
                <p class="mb-0">
                    Small steps for nature, big savings for you.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>